			(property "Description" "N-Channel Mosfet\n\nLEGEND\n\nVDS: Voltage Drain-Source ID: Drain Current RDS(ON): Drain-Source On-State Resistance VGS(TH): Gate-Source Threshold Voltage CISS: Drain-Source Input Capacitance\n\nSOT-23   Name VDS ID RDS(ON) VGS(TH) CISS Order Number    2N7002E 60V 260mA 2.5 Ohm 2.5V @ 250uA 26.7pF @ 25V 2N7002ET1GOSTR-ND    BSH103 30V 850mA 400 mOhm 400mV @ 1mA 83pF @ 24V BSH103,235-ND    BSS138 60V 320mA 1.6 Ohm 1.5V @ 250uA 50pF @ 10V Mouser: 771-BSS138PW115    DMN2075U-7 20V 4.2A 38 mOhm 1V @ 250 uA 594.3pF @ 10V DMN2075U-7DICT-ND\n\n* BSS138 good choice for I2C level-shifting\n\nPOWERPAK 1212-8   Name VDS ID RDS(ON) VGS(TH) CISS Order Number    Si7308DN 60V 6A 58 mOhm 3V @ 250uA 665pF @ 15V SI7308DN-T1-E3CT-ND"
